title="Alex Nelson">Alex Nelson</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Observe
<fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[\begin {align*}\sigma \lambda (a,\zeta ) &=\zeta ^{-1}\lambda (a,\zeta ) = \sigma (a + \zeta \sigma (a)+…+\zeta ^{n-1}\sigma ^{n-1}(a))\\ &=\zeta ^{-1}(\zeta \sigma (a)+\zeta ^{2}\sigma ^{2}(a)+…+\zeta ^{n-1}\sigma ^{n-1}(a)+a)\\ &=\zeta ^{-1}\lambda (a,\zeta ).\end {align*}]]></fr:tex>
Furthermore,
<fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[\begin {align*}\sigma (\lambda (a,\zeta )^{n}) &= \zeta ^{-n}\lambda (a,\zeta )^{n}\\ &=\lambda (a,\zeta )^{n}\end {align*}]]></fr:tex>
which implies <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\lambda (a,\zeta )^{n}\in \mathbb {F}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
<fr:p>If <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[b=\lambda (a,\zeta )^{n}]]></fr:tex>, then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\sqrt [n]{b}\in \Bbbk ]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[b\in \mathbb {F}]]></fr:tex>. Then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {F}(\sqrt [n]{b})=\Bbbk ]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
<fr:p>By the <fr:link
type="local"
href="nt-002T.xml"
addr="nt-002T"
title="Linear Independence of Characters">linear independence of characters</fr:link>, there exists an <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in \mathbb {F}]]></fr:tex> such that
<fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\lambda (a,\zeta )\neq 0]]></fr:tex> and
<fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[\sigma \lambda (a,\zeta )=\zeta ^{-1}\lambda (a,\zeta )\neq \lambda (a,\zeta ),]]></fr:tex>
so for any <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[k]]></fr:tex> we have
<fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[\sigma ^{k}\lambda (a,\zeta )=\zeta ^{-k}\lambda (a,\zeta )\neq \lambda (a,\zeta ).]]></fr:tex>
Hence <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\lambda (a,\zeta )]]></fr:tex> is not fixed by any subgroup of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathop {\textrm {Gal}}\nolimits (\Bbbk  / \mathbb {F})]]></fr:tex>. Hence <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\Bbbk =\mathbb {F}(\sqrt [n]{b})]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p><html:span
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
class="qed">∎</html:span></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter><fr:tree
